#: ../../source/optimization/5. analyze_optimization.md:1
msgid "优化结果的分析与使用"
msgstr "Analyzing and Using Optimization Results"

#: ../../source/optimization/5. analyze_optimization.md:3
msgid "结果分析"
msgstr "Result Analysis"

#: ../../source/optimization/5. analyze_optimization.md:5
msgid "从结果表中按**夏普**、**回撤**等列排序，比较不同参数组的稳定性与收益风险比。"
msgstr ""
"Sort the result table by **Sharpe ratio**, **drawdown**, and other columns to compare stability and "
"risk-return profiles across parameter sets."

#: ../../source/optimization/5. analyze_optimization.md:6
msgid "可绘制参数与目标函数的关系图（若支持），观察敏感性与局部最优。"
msgstr ""
"If supported, plot parameter–objective relationships to inspect sensitivity and local optima."

#: ../../source/optimization/5. analyze_optimization.md:8
msgid "目标函数与约束（罗列并简短解释）"
msgstr "Objectives and Constraints (with Brief Explanations)"

#: ../../source/optimization/5. analyze_optimization.md:10
msgid "**优化目标**：当前支持的如夏普最大化、回撤最小化、收益最大化等，以配置项或 API 为准。"
msgstr ""
"**Optimization objective**: Currently supported goals such as maximizing Sharpe ratio, minimizing "
"drawdown, or maximizing return; see configuration or API docs."

#: ../../source/optimization/5. analyze_optimization.md:11
msgid "**约束**：若有（如最大回撤上限、最小交易次数），在配置中指定；满足约束的解才参与排序。"
msgstr ""
"**Constraints**: If any (e.g., max drawdown limit or minimum trade count), set them in configuration; "
"only feasible solutions participate in ranking."

#: ../../source/optimization/5. analyze_optimization.md:13
msgid "将最优参数写回策略"
msgstr "Apply Best Parameters to the Strategy"

#: ../../source/optimization/5. analyze_optimization.md:15
msgid ""
"使用 **op.set_parameter(stg_id, pars=best_pars)** 将优化得到的最优参数应用到 "
"Operator，即可用同一 Operator 进行后续回测（mode=1）或实盘，无需手动改代码。"
msgstr ""
"Use **``op.set_parameter(stg_id, pars=best_pars)``** to apply optimized parameters to the ``Operator``; "
"the same ``Operator`` can then be used for backtesting (``mode=1``) or live trading without manual code "
"changes."

#: ../../source/optimization/5. analyze_optimization.md:17
msgid "注意事项"
msgstr "Caveats"

#: ../../source/optimization/5. analyze_optimization.md:19
msgid "**过拟合**：在样本内优化得到的参数可能在样本外表现变差，建议做样本外验证或滚动优化。"
msgstr ""
"**Overfitting**: In-sample optimized parameters may underperform out of sample; use out-of-sample "
"validation or rolling optimization."

#: ../../source/optimization/5. analyze_optimization.md:20
msgid "**样本内外**：可用不同时间区间做优化与验证。"
msgstr "**In-sample vs out-of-sample**: Use different date ranges for optimization and validation."

#: ../../source/optimization/5. analyze_optimization.md:21
msgid "**计算时间**：opti_sample_count 或迭代次数越大，耗时越长；可在精度与时间之间权衡。"
msgstr ""
"**Compute time**: Larger ``opti_sample_count`` or iteration counts take longer; balance accuracy against "
"runtime."
